dgard and Healing</span><hr size=1> I am puzzled. Day after day I see Midgard getting kicked on alot of servers.<br>
In fact on one server most of the high level Midgard players are asking to be moved. And yet, You guys made it work.<br>
<br>
From observation, I would say that most assualts fail because healing collapses.<br>
Either the Healer is killed by an INF or the Thane is so busy he forgets to heal.<br>
Then of course we have the Shaman.<br>
<br>
The trolls do just fine, right up to the point when suddenly their healing is yanked.<br>
Then the archers simply murder them. My question is,<br>
<br>
Is my observation correct? or what am I missing. I have no doubt that in straight<br>
up melee it is un-fun to stand next to a troll warrior.<br>
<br>
At level 24 scout I shot a purple skald at point blank range with critical 8 hit<br>
